Gamoro ("we", "our", or "us") operates various mobile games (the "Service"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.

1. Information Collection and Use
We do not collect any personally identifiable information (such as name, address, or phone number) directly from our users. However, our games may use third-party services that collect information used to identify you.

2. Third-Party Service Providers
To improve your gaming experience and provide certain functionalities, our games may integrate services from the following third-party providers:

Google Play Services: Used for achievements, leaderboards, and app updates.

Unity Technologies: Used for game engine performance analytics and crash reporting.

AdMob/Unity Ads (If applicable): Used to display advertisements within the games.

These third parties may collect information such as your device ID, IP address, and game activity. We encourage you to review their respective Privacy Policies.

3. Log Data
Whenever you use our Service, in the event of an error or crash, we collect data and information (through third-party products) on your phone called Log Data. This Log Data may include information such as your device Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, device name, operating system version, the configuration of the app when utilizing our Service, the time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics.

4. Children’s Privacy
Our Services do not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. In the case we discover that a child under 13 has provided us with personal information, we immediately delete this from our servers.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at: Email: [Masukkan Email Anda di Sini]
